Human (FancyHands):  $3-7/task    Complex escalations, disputes

# The orchestrator decides which executor handles each task.
# Same interface. Different cost. Different capability.
# A building call that Bland AI can't close after 2 attempts
# gets routed to FancyHands. The interface is the same:
# "Call [building] and confirm [details]."
# The executor swaps. The interface stays.</pre>
</div>

